        <ul>
          <li>You are responsible for your account</li>
          <li>Keep your login credentials secure</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Listings</h2>
        <p>
          Users can create and manage listings. You are responsible for the
          accuracy of your content.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Prohibited Activities</h2>
