        <h2>7. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms at any time. Continued use means acceptance.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>Email us at <strong>support@wanderlust.com</strong></p>

        <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
